<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Unit Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .content ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="header">Dear [Customer's Name],</p>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Congratulations! We are delighted to confirm your unit booking at <strong>[Project Name]</strong> <strong>[Phase/Block]</strong>. Here are the details of your booking:</p>

            <h3>Unit Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Unit Number:</span> [Unit Number]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Unit Size:</span> [Unit Size]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Unit Facing:</span> [Unit Face]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Booking Date:</span> [Date]</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Pricing Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Unit Price per Sq Yards:</span> [Unit Price]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Sale Value:</span> [Sale Value]</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Payment Milestones:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Booking Amount:</span> [Booking Amount]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">First Installment:</span> [Amount] due on [Date]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Second Installment:</span> [Amount] due on [Date]</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Final Payment:</span> [Amount] due on [Date]</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
            <p>Please keep your KYC documents ready. Our CRM team will reach out to you shortly to guide you through the process and answer any questions you might have.</p>

            <h3>Working Timings:</h3>
            <p>Our office hours are from <strong>[Working Hours]</strong>.</p>

            <h3>Terms and Conditions:</h3>
            <p>Cancellation policies and other terms can be found in the attached document.</p>

            <p>We look forward to assisting you in this exciting journey. Feel free to reach out to us if you need any further assistance.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="footer">Warm regards, <br> Epitome Projects LLP</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>